title: I'm back.
author: Ted Nivison
description:
I'm back. Let's talk about why I don't post often, and why I'm gonna be posting more. Be kind to yourselves, folks.

About Ted Nivison / JehBerDeh: 
Ted Nivison is a YouTube entertainer/Filmmaker/voice actor/comedian based in Los Angeles. He creates comedy videos on YouTube making commentary videos about various funny topics and poking fun at ridiculous people on Facebook, YouTube, and Instagram. He's got some sweet moves as well.
